name: Acid Colors #4
description:
Acid Colors is a reflection on the relationship we develop with colors from the perspective of an artist. It seeks to describe the sensations and processes that unfold from the eye and interact with the contents of the mind, in the creation of meaning.
It represents a state of personal investigation; about the influence that the different color frequencies print on our concept of reality.
It was made in Processing and exported with movie maker in MP4 format.
This NFT uses the sound compiled with the name of industrial sky.wav, from X3nus user of FreeSound platform. It is used under a Creative Common CCO 3.0 license, which you can consult here: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
